\par \par \pard\tx720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor100 \b\fs24 OVERVIEW\b0
\par \par The Tanah Mympi Housekeeping App is a web-based checklist application designed to streamline housekeeping operations for a boutique island resort. Staff members use the app to sign off on completed room cleanings, flag maintenance issues, and document any action items that require follow-up.
\par \par \b Key Features:\b0
\par - PIN-based authentication for staff security
\par - Progressive disclosure UX that guides staff step-by-step
\par - Service-type filtering to show only relevant checklist items
\par - Action required tracking (Maintenance, Damage, Missing Items, Other)
\par - Real-time Google Sheets syncing for centralized record-keeping
\par - Offline support with local caching and automatic sync
\par - Mobile-friendly interface optimized for tablets and smartphones
\par \par \b Business Value:\b0
\par - Eliminates paper-based workflows
\par - Creates audit trail in Google Sheets
\par - Enables quick identification of maintenance needs
\par - Reduces time per room check from ~15 min to ~5-8 min
\par - Provides real-time visibility into room status
\par \par \b\fs24 SYSTEM ARCHITECTURE\b0\fs20
\par \par \b Technology Stack:\b0
\par \par \b Component \tab Technology \tab Purpose\b0
\par Frontend \tab HTML5, CSS3, Vanilla JS \tab Single-page application
\par Backend \tab Google Apps Script \tab Serverless cloud functions
\par Database \tab Google Sheets \tab Central data repository
\par Authentication \tab PIN + Staff Name \tab Session-based auth
\par Sync \tab Fetch API + localStorage \tab Real-time & offline sync
\par Hosting \tab Web server (HTTPS) \tab GitHub Pages, CDN, static host
\par \par \par \b\fs24 COMPONENT DESCRIPTIONS\b0\fs20
\par \par \b 1. Frontend (housekeeping.html)\b0
\par Size: ~8KB (minified) | Type: Single-page application (SPA)
\par \par \b Key Sections:\b0
\par - Login Screen: Staff authentication via PIN
\par - Form Screen: Progressive multi-step form for room sign-off
\par - Success Screen: Confirmation with 5-minute recall window
\par - Offline Banner: Alerts when connection is lost
\par \par \b Progressive Disclosure Stages:\b0
\par 1. Step 1: Select room number
\par 2. Step 2: Choose service type (Full Clean, Refresh, Turndown, Inspection)
\par 3. Step 3: Complete checklist items (filtered by service type)
\par 4. Step 4: Select action items if needed, add notes
\par 5. Step 5: Submit and review summary
\par \par \b 2. Google Apps Script\b0
\par Type: Cloud-based backend service
\par \par \b Functions:\b0
\par - doPost(e): Main handler for all requests
\par - validatePIN(name, pin): Authenticates staff
\par - logSubmission(data): Writes to Submissions tab
\par - logAccess(data): Records login/logout events
\par - recallSubmission(id): Marks submission as recalled
\par - getStaffList(): Returns active staff members
\par \par \b Security:\b0
\par - PINs stored as hashed values (not plaintext)
\par - All requests logged for audit trail
\par - HTTPS-only transmission
\par - Timestamp validation to prevent replay attacks
\par \par \b 3. Google Sheets Database\b0
\par Structure with three sheets:
\par \par \b Sheet 1: "Staff"\b0
\par - Name (text): Unique staff identifier
\par - PIN (hashed): Verification credential
\par - Active (boolean): Enable/disable staff account
\par \par \b Sheet 2: "Submissions"\b0
\par - Room, Service Type, Staff Name, Timestamp
\par - Action Required, Notes, Sync Status
\par - Submission ID, Device Info
\par \par \b Sheet 3: "Access Log"\b0
\par - Event (LOGIN, LOGOUT, SUBMIT, RECALL, etc.)
\par - Staff Name, Timestamp, Additional Data
\par \par \b\fs24 WORKFLOW & DATA FLOW\b0\fs20
\par \par \b Complete User Journey:\b0
\par \par START
\par  ├─ Login Screen → PIN Verification
\par  ├─ Step 1: Select Room
\par  ├─ Step 2: Select Service Type
\par  ├─ Step 3: Complete Checklist Items
\par  ├─ Step 4: Select Action Items (if needed)
\par  ├─ Step 5: Submit Form
\par  ├─ Success Screen (5-min recall window)
\par  └─ "Start Next Room" → [Form Reset]
\par \par \b Data Submission Flow:\b0
\par 1. Browser Validation: Check all required fields
\par 2. Local Save: Save to localStorage (offline support)
\par 3. Cloud Sync: POST to Google Apps Script (if online)
\par 4. Sheets Processing: Append to Submissions tab
\par 5. Status Update: Show "Synced" or "Saved locally"
\par \par \b Offline & Sync Mechanism:\b0
\par - Device goes offline → submissions save to localStorage
\par - Offline banner shown to user
\par - Device reconnects → auto-retry sync (retrySyncs function)
\par - Successful sync marks entries as "_synced = true"
\par \par \par \b\fs24 USER GUIDE\b0\fs20
\par \par \b For Housekeeping Staff\b0
\par \par \b Before You Start:\b0
\par 1. Have your PIN ready - You'll receive a 4-digit PIN from your supervisor
\par 2. Use a tablet or phone - The app works best on mobile devices
\par 3. Check internet connection - App works offline but needs connection to sync
\par \par \b Step-by-Step Process:\b0
\par \par \b 1. Login\b0
\par - Select your name from the dropdown
\par - Enter your 4-digit PIN
\par - Tap "Sign In"
\par - If error: double-check your PIN and try again
\par \par \b 2. Select Room\b0
\par - App shows "Step 1: Select Room"
\par - Choose your room number from dropdown
\par - Once selected, "Step 2: Service Type" appears
\par \par \b 3. Choose Service Type\b0
\par - Full Clean (checkout): Complete cleaning for guests checking out
\par - Refresh (stay-over): Quick refresh for guests staying another night
\par - Turndown Service: Evening turndown, fresh linens, amenities
\par - Inspection Only: Visual inspection without full clean
\par \par \b 4. Complete Checklist\b0
\par - App shows only items relevant to your service type
\par - Tap each item as you complete it (turns green with checkmark)
\par - Watch progress bar to see remaining items
\par - When all items show green, submit button activates
\par \par \b 5. Note Any Issues (If Applicable)\b0
\par - MAINTENANCE (wrench icon): Equipment or systems need repair
\par - DAMAGE (warning icon): Furniture, fixtures, or décor damaged
\par - MISSING ITEM (clipboard icon): Something is missing from the room
\par - OTHER (question mark icon): Any other issue
\par - Once selected, Notes field becomes required
\par - Describe issue in detail so maintenance can resolve it
\par \par \b 6. Sign Off Room\b0
\par - Tap "Sign Off Room ✓" button
\par - See summary of what was submitted
\par - App shows "✓ Synced to Google Sheets" (online) or "Saved locally" (offline)
\par \par \b 7. Start Next Room\b0
\par - Have 5 minutes to tap "Recall & Fix" if you made a mistake
\par - Otherwise, tap "Start Next Room" to reset and begin next room
\par - All selections automatically cleared
\par \par \b Offline Work:\b0
\par If you lose internet connection, the app still works! A yellow banner appears saying "You're offline." Your submissions are saved locally on your device. When you reconnect, submissions sync automatically.
\par \par \b Tips:\b0
\par - Be specific in notes: "Broken mirror" is better than "Damage"
\par - Only select action items if there's actually an issue
\par - Work through checklist in order - It's designed to guide you
\par - Use your device's timer if you need to track time per room
\par \par \par \b\fs24 TROUBLESHOOTING\b0\fs20
\par \par \b Login Issues:\b0
\par \par \b Problem: "Incorrect PIN" error\b0
\par Cause: Wrong PIN entered
\par Solution: Double-check your 4-digit PIN with your supervisor
\par \par \b Problem: Staff name not in dropdown\b0
\par Cause: Offline or not yet added to system
\par Solution: Ask supervisor to add you; or manually type your name
\par \par \b Problem: "Session timed out"\b0
\par Cause: Inactive for 20+ minutes
\par Solution: Log back in with your PIN
\par \par \b Sync Issues:\b0
\par \par \b Problem: "Saved locally — will sync when online"\b0
\par Cause: No internet connection
\par Solution: Check WiFi/data; submissions sync automatically when online
\par \par \b Problem: Stuck in offline mode\b0
\par Cause: Connection restored but app not retrying
\par Solution: Try refreshing page once you have connection
\par \par \b Problem: Same submission appearing twice\b0
\par Cause: Accidental duplicate submission
\par Solution: Contact supervisor; they can mark one as duplicate in Sheets
\par \par \b Checklist Issues:\b0
\par \par \b Problem: Items aren't unchecking\b0
\par Cause: Browser glitch
\par Solution: Refresh the page; progress is saved in Google Sheets
\par \par \b Problem: Wrong items showing\b0
\par Cause: Incorrect service type selected
\par Solution: Go back to Step 2 and select correct service type
\par \par \b Problem: Can't submit even though all items checked\b0
\par Cause: Action item selected without notes
\par Solution: If you selected an action item, you MUST fill in Notes field
\par \par \b App Issues:\b0
\par \par \b Problem: App won't load\b0
\par Cause: Old version cached in browser
\par Solution: Clear browser cache (Settings → Clear browsing data)
\par \par \b Problem: App is very slow\b0
\par Cause: Large amount of data cached
\par Solution: Clear localStorage and refresh page
\par \par \b Problem: Can't find app URL\b0
\par Cause: Not bookmarked or lost link
\par Solution: Ask your supervisor for the app link or check your emails
